name: Neural Glitch Portrait #2
description: Artist: Mario Klingemann / @Quasimondo | In 2018 I began experimenting with deliberately mutating and blending the learned weights inside of neural networks I had previously trained.  I call this technique of latent lobotomy "Neural Glitch". Unlike the classic technique of glitching a single image by manipulating the bytes of a saved file this method causes the damaged model to continuously generate misinterpretations on a textural as well as a semantic level.  PNG, 2048x2048 pixels Original creation date: August 29th 2018
